messages.message: Hey everyone! I am collecting a list of all topics and entities that we have looked to extract from documents, or would like to extract from documents, which is often an ask from third parties who would like to experiment with putting their models on Instabase. I would really appreciate it if you could add to this list. https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1brqviCImnk2xKPNq66cXjYWn-84o3HO69A4dM7cWrYI/edit?usp=sharing
